# Help / discovery

- **Docs:** Adding/changing nodes → update **`src/data/node-documentation.json`** (`"node:<id>"`). **`title`** matches **`NodeSpec.displayName`** (casing rules: **`shaders/node-standards.mdc`**). Full checklist: **`node-standards.mdc`**.
- **Help UI:** Enabled when **exactly one** node selected; otherwise disabled / alternate messaging.
- **Context menu:** _Read Guide_ (same payload as Help), _Copy node name_ (type id), _Remove_ (node + wires); non-blocking.

**Refs:** `docs/node-documentation-content-guide.md`, `docs/user-goals/10-help-and-discovery.md`.
